ign reference of the emerging paradigm thanks to the interiorised practice of it. There is pa amb tomàquet and delicious wine too! We are celebrating as well our client’s successes, their leading roles in their own fields on the transition to a sustainable society in planet Earth make us really proud of them. It is a also a reason to celebrate the healthy group of people we are as holoners. We are grateful for all people who passed by the coop as diving board to their own life-changing initiatives."}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"heading-2","key":"cbd3f31e5bce44f691f5a7a4dd82d518","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"ebd9c6f92c3f42bca97f94632733ad21","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":"Focus areas "}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"16350c48c8ff48bba5692f260d1c6a15","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"39da680487b146efb7bcace718206607","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[{"kind":"mark","data":{},"type":"italic"}],"text":"Where are we putting our attention? "}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"list-unordered","key":"05a2388353674bc2aed8cd5f8425a3b9","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"block","type":"list-item","key":"aadaaff4a03f42f3af3700009fbdddbc","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"530821c261ee4163ab352ecde5c45022","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"05d867bef09e4f57878efe07db471e12","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":"To be a healthy and content-with-euphoria group of people"}]}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"list-item","key":"9c1afb722e834c999e62615bebd9b8ef","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"295cb80baacb466caa2352ef4593b52e","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"55c83344cdfb41028ee9f9df202236e3","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":"To contribute to organisations we share purpose with"}]}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"list-item","key":"ab7594b7d5744b0189f944a3ad1d0108","isVo