a":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"159b0b120aef42279ee13bc5daa203c1","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":"Although in some part of this world a happy and comfortable life is achievable, we recognise that as a whole, there is a lot of work to do. In the territories where there is still suffering, and in the content societies where some dynamics are responsible for some of the sufferings elsewhere. "}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"3504e02d6a3e4eb7917c681282a3613f","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"e9171243f94a45c19dd22802f123010d","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":"Our shared consciousness of a planetary society drives us to act upon it. Our purposeful actions though are not understood as a duty or a hard task. Our experience is that aligning action and purpose is a sign of freedom, furthermore, is fulfilling and the perfect setting for endless fun. This joyful approach to every moment is, finally, what keep us going. Our brain and body is never as creative as when we are positive about the impact we have!"}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"d058e068b1df42aca220939c13f21607","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"7d6d9eb98f3a4dfda227a0dc4d85d066","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":""}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"ec7fab9ffd504283a182c55d7c88ef09","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"a058f91eb58c49109232f7d885bd2bfc","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":"Barcelona, November 2014"}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"50bf18cd0d1444bba5b249c758a298dd","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"b08b464abc9548bdbcd8480890459d6e","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":" .   "}]}]},{"kind":"block","type":"paragraph","key":"ba4a43f274724c1fb70cadb4fb96d41f","isVoid":false,"data":{},"nodes":[{"kind":"text","key":"8502bbaffa434d6e843fd04b5b393603","ranges":[{"kind":"range","marks":[],"text":"  "}]}]},{"kind":"bloc